vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of Tracy Street, formerly known as Taylor Street, to McKinney Webb Holdings, LLC, the abutting owner, containing approximately 2,593 square feet of land, located near its intersection with Webb Avenue; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Capital Reserve Fund ($608,154.00) and General Fund ($20,000.00), plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
